oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Board for the East Nashville Urban Renewal Project on a Field Trip, 1959
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Photograph of the board for the East Nashville Urban Renewal Project (Project Tenn. R-13) on a bus for a field trip, 28 April 1959. Pictured left to right: J. Green, W.J. Diehl, Dr. I.L. Moore, Gerald Gimre, M. Howell, J.P. Grimes, G. Guy, Floyd Adkisson, and C.M. Taggart. Forms part of the MDHA Photograph Collection. 1 photograph : b & w.
